### Get all family groups
GET http://localhost:5120/api/GruposFamiliares

### Get family groups by albergue
GET http://localhost:5120/api/GruposFamiliares/albergue/1

### Get all albergues to test
GET http://localhost:5120/api/Albergues

### Get all municipios to test
GET http://localhost:5120/api/Municipios